'''維多利亞·佩德雷蒂'''（{{lang-en|Victoria Pedretti}}，{{bd|1995年|3月23日}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.msn.com/en-au/entertainment/tv/who-is-victoria-pedretti-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-star-of-you-season-two/ar-BBYnI8N|title=Who Is Victoria Pedretti? Everything You Need To Know About The New Star Of 'YOU' Season Two|last=Wahi|first=Sukriti|work=MSN Entertainment|date=December 27, 2019|access-date=May 9, 2020|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006041217/https://www.msn.com/en-au/entertainment/tv/who-is-victoria-pedretti-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-star-of-you-season-two/ar-BBYnI8N/|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一位[[美國|美國]][[女演員|女演員]]。2018年於[[Netflix|Netflix]]影集《[[鬼入侵|鬼入侵]]》中飾演克蘭家雙胞胎的妹妹尼爾而知名。<ref name="Casting1">{{cite web|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|title=''The Haunting Of Hill House'': Lulu Wilson & Victoria Pedretti Cast In Netflix Series Re-Imagining|url=https://deadline.com/2017/09/the-haunting-of-hill-house-lulu-wilson-victoria-pedretti-netflix-series-adaptation-1202170033/|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=September 14, 2017|accessdate=October 22, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710195024/https://deadline.com/2017/09/the-haunting-of-hill-house-lulu-wilson-victoria-pedretti-netflix-series-adaptation-1202170033/|archive-date=July 10, 2018|}}</ref>

== 早年經歷 ==
佩德雷蒂在[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]的[[費城|費城]]出生，她的父親是一名擁有[[意大利|意大利]]血統的[[教授|教授]]。她的外祖母是[[德系猶太人|德系猶太人]]，佩德雷蒂曾舉行過[[猶太教成人禮|猶太教成人禮]]。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Rice |first1=Lilyanne |title=Inside Victoria Pedretti's life, her parents and boyfriend |url=https://www.stylesrant.com/inside-victoria-pedretti-life/ |website=stylesrant.com |access-date=18 November 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128075010/https://www.stylesrant.com/inside-victoria-pedretti-life/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
佩德雷蒂表示她在一個情感虐待的家庭中長大，但當談到她的父母時則說：「非常愛他們，他們已經盡了最大努力」。<ref>{{Citation|title=Victoria Pedretti Laughs and Cries Her Way to Accepting The Gift of Her Sensitivity|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TG4hX6LBMjI|language=en|access-date=2022-02-04}}</ref> 她在六歲時被診斷患有[[專注力失調或過度活躍症|專注力失調或過度活躍症]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/article/victoria-pedretti-interview-2020|title='People tried to tell me about my own mind my entire life': Star of Netflix's 'You' & The Haunting of Bly Manor, Victoria Pedretti, powerfully opens up about having ADD|last=Smith|first=Josh|work=[[Glamour_(magazine)|Glamour]]|date=October 26, 2020|access-date=December 6, 2020|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428065316/https://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/article/victoria-pedretti-interview-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>
她在2017年從[[卡尼基美隆大學|卡尼基美隆大學]]的戲劇學院畢業。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://drama.cmu.edu/victoria-pedretti/ |title=Victoria Pedretti |date=October 22, 2018 |website=Carnegie Mellon University School of Drama |access-date=October 23, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023120109/https://drama.cmu.edu/victoria-pedretti/ |archive-date=October 23, 2018 | }}</ref>

== 職業生涯 ==
佩德雷蒂於2014年開始表演生涯，她在大學時期出演過兩部獨立短片。2018年，她在[[Netflix|Netflix]]影集《[[鬼入侵|鬼入侵]]》中飾演尼爾·克蘭，演技獲得評論家的好評，也獲得了[[土星獎|土星獎]]和[[MTV影視大獎|MTV影視大獎]]的提名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thethings.com/netflix-praises-victoria-pedrettis-performance-in-the-haunting-of-bly-manor/|title=Netflix Praises Victoria Pedretti's Performance In 'The Haunting Of Bly Manor'|last=Sarrubba|first=Stefania|work=The Things|date=October 12, 2020|access-date=October 22, 2020|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218143137/https://www.thethings.com/netflix-praises-victoria-pedrettis-performance-in-the-haunting-of-bly-manor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，她在[[昆汀·塔倫蒂諾|昆汀·塔倫蒂諾]]執導的喜劇戲劇電影《[[從前，有個荷里活|從前，有個荷里活]]》中出演暱稱露露的萊斯利·範·侯登（Leslie Van Houten）。<ref name="Casting2">{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/charles-manson-damon-herriman-quentin-tarantino-once-upon-time-hollywood-rumer-willis/|title=''Once Upon a Time in Hollywood'' Adds Rumer Willis, Margaret Qualley and Damon Herriman|last=Gonzalez|first=Umberto|date=August 28, 2018|website=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829110013/https://www.thewrap.com/charles-manson-damon-herriman-quentin-tarantino-once-upon-time-hollywood-rumer-willis/|archive-date=August 29, 2018|accessdate=January 30, 2019}}</ref>同樣在2019年，佩德雷蒂在Netflix發布的影集《[[安眠書店_(電視劇)|安眠書店]]》的第二季中飾演富家女樂芙·奎因<ref name="Casting3">{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/you-victoria-pedretti-cast-female-lead-season-2-netflix-1202545163/|title=''You'': Victoria Pedretti Cast As the Female Lead In Series' Second Season On Netflix|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=January 30, 2019|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=January 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190130212631/https://deadline.com/2019/01/you-victoria-pedretti-cast-female-lead-season-2-netflix-1202545163/|archive-date=January 30, 2019|}}</ref>。

2020年，佩德雷蒂客串了[[Apple_TV+|Apple TV+]][[網絡劇集|網絡劇集]]《[[幻異傳奇|幻異傳奇]]》中第一集的Evelyn Porter，並於同年在傳記電影《雪莉》（Shirley）中飾演凱瑟琳（Katherine）受到評論家好評。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-06|title=Movie Review – Shirley (2020)|url=https://www.flickeringmyth.com/2020/06/movie-review-shirley-2020-2/|access-date=2020-06-18|website=Flickering Myth|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Shirley (2020)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shirley_2020|language=en|access-date=2020-06-18|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106162012/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shirley_2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>其後亦在Netflix電視劇《[[鬼莊園|鬼莊園]]》中出演女主角丹妮爾·克萊頓。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/victoria-pedretti-star-the-haunting-of-bly-manor-anthology-series-cast-netflix-1202639440/|title=Victoria Pedretti To Headline 'The Haunting of Bly Manor' Netflix Series|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=June 28, 2019|access-date=June 29, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629034711/https://deadline.com/2019/06/victoria-pedretti-star-the-haunting-of-bly-manor-anthology-series-cast-netflix-1202639440/|archive-date=June 29, 2019|}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2019/06/28/haunting-of-hill-house-season-2-cast-victoria-pedretti-bly-manor/|title=Hill House's Victoria Pedretti Returning for Netflix's The Haunting of Bly Manor|last=Swift|first=Andy|work=TVLine|date=June 28, 2019|access-date=June 29, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629104258/https://tvline.com/2019/06/28/haunting-of-hill-house-season-2-cast-victoria-pedretti-bly-manor/|archive-date=June 29, 2019|}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/video/netflix-the-haunting-of-bly-manor-sets-launch-first-teaser/|title=Netflix’s ‘The Haunting Of Bly Manor’ Sets Launch Date, Offers First Teaser|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Bruce|last=Haring|date=August 31, 2020|access-date=October 8, 2020|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831172143/https://deadline.com/video/netflix-the-haunting-of-bly-manor-sets-launch-first-teaser/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

她將在《[[安眠書店_(電視劇)|安眠書店]]》第三季中回歸出演樂芙·奎因，該影集預定於2021年首播。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiotimes.com/news/on-demand/2019-11-11/you-season-2-netflix-release-date/|title=When is You series two released on Netflix?|last=Carr|first=Flora|work=Radio Times|date=November 11, 2019|access-date=November 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111164732/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/on-demand/2019-11-11/you-season-2-netflix-release-date/|archive-date=November 11, 2019|}}</ref>

